mg src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a337e0b8ca7a32721eaefcb9d5ce919ec321bffd","tid":1845361,"uid":164730,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"阻止中國觀光客的方法只有薩德了，快點增加薩德和射擊訓練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690cf330e9bd3380b5b9a3096d7d0c933304e8d5","tid":1845361,"uid":126283,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e14c9df3134f6ee33b28b1fed2257722f85034d6","tid":1845361,"uid":19278,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:22:54.000Z","msg":"致癌的懸浮微粒已經讓人很不爽了，現在還來病毒，真是麻煩的垃圾國家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"全球反支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持支那繼續累人累物<br />\n到時黎個全球殺支令<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4910e226ecaebfb33926e8efd3840870e6a7d9","tid":1845361,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:28:35.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=428366aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"f22bd82c4e7e69a124f0d56d6a8311a7995b868e","tid":1845361,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:29:00.000Z","msg":"日本"},{"pid":"021c6794e60b41b462e7dadf32aba17b430e8567","tid":1845361,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"baa1878755883e77cba906848dea33694feebea9","tid":1845361,"uid":32511,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"zuaf****：他們說2千人，其實是說6千人<br />\n-mk78****：乘以100就行了，冠狀病毒時（SARS）也說有2000人中，實際揭露後是24萬人<br />\n 呵<br />\n-aaxx****：至少超過2萬人<br />\n-wlst****：武漢500名韓僑中有2人中... 0.4%... 1100萬人口的武漢乘以這機率的話？4<br />\n萬4千人....<br />\n-sr01****：6千，那中國人也太善良了 呵呵 最少2萬<br />\n <br />\nzxc7****：蟑螂們 地球的敵人<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n：台灣送回所有湖北觀光客+罰款：<br />\n <br />\nlamm****：聽說台灣罰了隱匿病情入國的人一千萬，我們也要強硬開罰，阻止病毒擴散<br />\n-tibe****：聽說台灣還禁止中國觀光客入境<br />\n-jinh****：台灣難波萬<br />\n <br />\nodg6****：哎 真羨慕~~<br />\n <br />\ntalr****：這才是正常的國家<br />\n <br />\n7eej****：我們政府在幹什麼？不照顧我國國民嗎？又在看中國臉色嗎？真鬱悶，真是<br />\n... （我）反中親美<br />\n <br />\nicdi****：台灣確實做的比我國好呢 親中舔北的文白痴叫我們別緊張 所以更令人緊張<br />\n <br />\nsheo****：聽說現在政府因為習近平要訪韓而看他們的臉色，所以把湖北武漢改成灰色警報（禁止旅行）還要看他們臉色。先有國民才有外交，（文）總統這人比起國民的心情，更害怕習近平的心情不好呢<br />\n <br />\ncxen****：現在韓國有15萬人... 要怎麼辦<br />\n（新聞是說，光是2020年1月就有13萬中國遊客去韓國玩）<br />\n <br />\nsesi****：羨慕台灣政府的應對措施<br />\n <br />\ntomo****：台灣加油，我們也要學習台灣的氣魄！<br />\n <br />\ndino****：台灣政府比我國要更讚呢！<br />\n <br />\nsun2****: good 759, bad 89<br />\n文在寅 學學吧<br />\n <br />\nange****: good 337, bad 23<br />\n為什麼青瓦台這麼安靜？國民正在請願禁止中國人入境，請大家參加<br />\n <br />\nwasi****：看到這個真覺得台灣是先進國家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:29:53.000Z","msg":"聯署？"},{"pid":"a884a3ccfc7824c25d1c0ccd0af71